These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, pop, folk, r&b, blues, funk, reggae
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of r&b is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 6. the american is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 7. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of pop and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the fan of blues and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
14. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
15. the fan of blues is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Music-Genre          | folk    | techno    | pop | funk | r&b | blues    | reggae |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

