 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the horse is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
 6. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 9. the owner of the rabbit is not the person drinking fanta##6
10. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
11. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
14. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the ferret##1
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
16. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
